data.description: Welcome to 1114 Clemson St, a meticulously maintained residence offering both convenience and versatility. This 4/5 bedroom, 2.5 bathroom home is strategically located near major highways including I-95 and I-495, as well as the train station, ensuring easy commuting and access to amenities.  There is also the ability to add another bathroom on the entry level as it is already setup for one!!  Key Features:  Versatile Entry Level: The house features an entry-level setup that can effortlessly be transformed into an in-law suite, providing flexibility for different living arrangements.  Expansive Layout: Enjoy the benefits of an open floor plan, providing a seamless flow between living spaces. This design enhances both functionality and a sense of spaciousness.  Coveted Loft on 4th Floor: Discover the allure of a loft space on the 4th floor, perfect for a bedroom, workout room, or any other purpose that suits your lifestyle. This additional area adds a unique touch to the home.  Convenient Location: Situated near major highways and the train station, this home ensures easy access to transportation, making your daily commute a breeze.  2.5 Bathrooms: Practicality meets comfort with 2.5 well-appointed bathrooms, offering convenience for both residents and guests.  2 Car Garage: Experience the luxury of a two-car garage, providing secure parking and additional storage space.  This property at 1114 Clemson St is a rare find, offering a blend of convenience, versatility, and modern living. Don't miss the opportunity to make this your dream home. Schedule a showing today!  Or, you can immediately check out the Video Walkthrough and 3D mapping of the house, just search for the address and you should be good to go!  Built by Montchanin Builders.   Note: Square footage, room dimensions, and other property details are approximate and should be independently verified.
